---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import PageHead from "../../components/PageHead.astro";
const updated = "February 20, 2026";
---

<Layout>
  <style>
    .page-wrap h1 {
      font-size: var(--text-xxl);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .page-wrap h2 {
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .page-wrap p {
      margin: 1rem 0;
      font-size: var(--text-base);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .subhead {
      color: var(--kbm-green);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
    }

    /* ===== Responsive Banner / Placeholder ===== */
    .banner {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--kbm-green), var(--kbm-green-2));
      color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;

      /* desktop height */
      min-height: 260px;

      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    /* inner text wrapper so we can style headline/text later next to an image */
    .banner-content {
      max-width: 600px;
    }

    .banner-title {
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.3;
      letter-spacing: 0.4px;
      margin: 0 0 .5rem 0;
    }

    .banner-note {
      font-size: var(--text-base);
      line-height: 1.4;
      opacity: 0.9;
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* space reserved for future headshot / product image */
    .banner-photo {
      position: absolute;
      right: 1.5rem;
      bottom: 1.5rem;
      width: 96px;
      height: 96px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: var(--text-base);
      font-weight: 600;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    /* On smaller screens: shorter banner, photo drops below text so it doesn't overlap */
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .banner {
        min-height: 180px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }

      .banner-photo {
        position: static;
        width: 80px;
        height: 80px;
        margin: 1rem auto 0 auto;
      }

      .banner-content {
        max-width: 100%;
      }
    }

    /* ===== Card Grid ===== */
    .card-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .card-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .card-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    .card {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
      color: #111827;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: var(--text-base);
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    /* ===== Let's Connect box ===== */
    .connect {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    .connect h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: var(--kbm-green);
    }

    .connect a {
      color: var(--kbm-green);
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* ===== Back to top button ===== */
    #kbm-top {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 30px;
      right: 30px;
      width: 46px;
      height: 46px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--kbm-green);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
      opacity: 0;
      visibility: hidden;
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease, visibility 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
      z-index: 9999;
    }

    #kbm-top.show {
      opacity: 1;
      visibility: visible;
    }

    #kbm-top:hover {
      background: var(--kbm-green-2);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .page-wrap p {
        line-height: 1.7;
      }
      
      .banner {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }
      
      .card {
        padding: 1.25rem;
      }
      
      .connect {
        padding: 1.25rem;
      }
    }
  </style>

  <div class="page-wrap">
  <PageHead
    title="About Knit it Now"
    breadcrumb="Home / About"
    subhead="15+ years helping knitters like you."
  />

  <p>
    <strong>Knit It Now</strong> is built on years of experience supporting knitters who want to feel confident with their machines.
  </p>

  <p>
    My goal is to take away the overwhelm and give you practical tools, resources, and encouragement so you can focus on creating projects you love.
  </p>

  <h2>My Story</h2>
  <p>
    I'm <strong>Sue Jalowiec</strong>, and for more than 15 years, I've been helping knitters overcome the challenges of machine knitting — from confusing instructions to projects that don't quite turn out as planned.
  </p>
  <p>
    That experience has shaped everything here at <strong>Knit It Now</strong> , where the goal is simple: to give you the confidence and support you need to succeed with your machine.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Knit It Now</strong>  is designed for knitters like you. It's a place where you'll find practical tools, clear resources, and encouraging guidance — all aimed at removing the guesswork so you can knit with confidence and actually enjoy the projects you start.
  </p>

  <h2>What You'll Discover</h2>
  <p>Here's a quick look at what you'll discover inside <strong><strong>Knit It Now</strong> </strong>:</p>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Patterns & Wizards</h3>
      <p>Custom-fit, step-by-step projects for any machine.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Tutorials & Tips</h3>
      <p>Practical techniques explained clearly.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Reference</h3>
      <p>Charts, tools, and guides all in one place.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Support for All Levels</h3>
      <p>Confidence for beginners and inspiration for experienced knitters.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p style="margin-top:2rem;">
    Machine knitting doesn't have to feel overwhelming. With clear steps and the right tools, you can knit with confidence and enjoy the process.
    That's what <strong>Knit It Now</strong>  is here to give you — clarity, confidence, and encouragement.
  </p>

  <div class="connect">
    <h2>Let's Connect</h2>
    <p>
      If you'd like help, have a question, or just want to say hello, I'd love to hear from you.<br />
      Reach out anytime at <a href="mailto:contact@knititnow.com">contact@knititnow.com</a>.
    </p>
  </div>

  <button id="kbm-top" aria-label="Back to top">↑</button>

  <script>
    const topBtn = document.getElementById("kbm-top");
    window.addEventListener("scroll", () => {
      if (window.scrollY > 200) topBtn.classList.add("show");
      else topBtn.classList.remove("show");
    });
    topBtn.addEventListener("click", () => {
      window.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: "smooth" });
    });
  </script>
  </div>
</Layout>
